{"tid":687471,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我執到阿拉丁神燈，而精靈又俾一個願望我","createTime":"2018-06-02T09:38:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-02T10:18:50.000Z","uid":51738,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"17231c149d02a65a53b94b6353f1aa32628deb91","tid":687471,"uid":51738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:38:08.000Z","msg":"我唔要咩無限金錢，世界和平之類19公式願望<br />\n<br />\n我只要<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">喺條街吸煙做火車頭既仆街，每食一枝煙就永久失去10%肺功能</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔洗你死，食兩三枝就會呼吸困難，等你班仆街感受吓冇食煙既人平時吸入你噴出黎啲煙有幾慘！<br />\n<br />\n食煙講真好難唔影響人，食完都仲係臭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而且二手/三手煙都係會令人增加患癌機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n收手啦煙剷們！"},{"pid":"c477a70fdcc37ca0d9a33897bde7bdd6bd4f79c0","tid":687471,"uid":175213,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:40:26.000Z","msg":"食煙正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59afecad724284ce5e316fb9345adb53a794f487","tid":687471,"uid":50744,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:41:26.000Z","msg":"要錢啦on9"},{"pid":"6771d2ff7e8374b9240fd8aa5af7d79cb0fac6bb","tid":687471,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa2f739af84677958aaa749b583245a1de2c1b5e","tid":687471,"uid":51738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6771d2ff7e8374b9240fd8aa5af7d79cb0fac6bb","tid":687471,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T09:58:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:06:01.000Z","msg":"見到你手5p殘體字，即刻想洗眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c4320404df19f43133b27669e7d21b74627aaea","tid":687471,"uid":137361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-02T10:10:05.000Z",